{"tid":1546290,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"繪本介紹！！大人小朋友都適合睇繪本","createTime":"2019-09-06T08:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T09:00:21.000Z","uid":234159,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f62ccd27b07755f9b0e93f0655bf55f3b79a34f","tid":1546290,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:32:29.000Z","msg":"三個大學生開了個介紹繪本的page，大家可以like 下😊<br />\n<br />\n我們相信：繪本的「力量」。不論是小朋友、大人，繪本當中的故事都深深與我們真實的生命互動，陪伴我們經歷迷惘和掙扎，盼望和成長，教育我們如何活得更好。我們希望以一顆最純粹的心，向大家介紹「好繪本」。歡迎大家一起交流！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Education-Website/%E7%B9%AA%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E6%A8%B9-408703159907834/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpages%2Fcategory%2FEducation-Website%2F%25E7%25B9%25AA%25E6%259C%25AC%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD%25E6%25A8%25B9-408703159907834%2F&d=%2B76N%2F2LucaPHjeWFFloOr34WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=f3582a0f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pages/category/Education-Website/%E7%B9%AA%E6%9C%AC%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD%E6%A8%B9-408703159907834/</a>"},{"pid":"fc0d2d0aff3032fcc9cfe6b90f7021202af77438","tid":1546290,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:33:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"da17b4fad6f40dc08e8c534d2f46dc13cdccc260","tid":1546290,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-06T08:35:09.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVeJJ3id.jpg&h=50bde3c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5dd757a3b5d30965dc64f63b42965c5415bef959",